<text id="02-output-contract" title="rust-testing-unit Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema (draft-07) for the code artefact this methodology produces, with valid and invalid examples and forbidden patterns.</summary>

  <section title="Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/rust-testing-unit.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": [
    "test_module_path",
    "is_colocated_cfg_test",
    "tokio_flavor",
    "uses_expect_messages"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "test_module_path": {
      "type": "string",
      "pattern": "\\.rs$"
    },
    "is_colocated_cfg_test": {
      "type": "boolean"
    },
    "tokio_flavor": {
      "enum": [
        "current_thread",
        "multi_thread"
      ]
    },
    "uses_expect_messages": {
      "const": true
    },
    "mocks_only_traits": {
      "const": true
    },
    "uses_virtual_time": {
      "type": "boolean"
    }
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "test_module_path": "src/service/user.rs",
  "is_colocated_cfg_test": true,
  "tokio_flavor": "current_thread",
  "uses_expect_messages": true,
  "mocks_only_traits": true,
  "uses_virtual_time": true
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "test_module_path": "tests/inline_test.rs",
  "is_colocated_cfg_test": false,
  "tokio_flavor": "none",
  "uses_expect_messages": false,
  "mocks_only_traits": false,
  "uses_virtual_time": false
}
]]></code>
    <note>No tokio flavor declared; uses unwrap() instead of expect; mocks a concrete struct.</note>
  </example>

  <section title="Forbidden">
    <forbidden id="f1">unwrap() inside a #[test] without a clear context.</forbidden>
    <forbidden id="f2">Default tokio runtime flavor (#[tokio::test] without the flavor argument).</forbidden>
    <forbidden id="f3">std::thread::sleep or real tokio::time::sleep used to coordinate test timing.</forbidden>
    <forbidden id="f4">mockall::mock! invocations against concrete (non-trait) types.</forbidden>
  </section>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-rust-testing-unit.py">Validator script.</reference>
</text>
